These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, australian, dutch, japanese
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is between the indonesian and the australian##2
3. the japanese is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | australian | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, papaya, blueberry, cherry
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | papaya | eggplant | cherry | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, action, fantasy, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific | fantasy | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, cricket, cycling
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | biathlon | cycling | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, weightlifting, skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | volleyball | badminton | skiing | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, polish, argentine
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the polish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | canadian | argentine | japanese |

