.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, metal, soul
1. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of blues is between the fan of jazz and the fan of metal##2
3. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | jazz | blues | metal |

