.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, subway, quad-bike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | subway | bus | quad-bike | helicopter |

