.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | coffee | iced-tea | almond-milk | tea |

