3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
4. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | volleyball | climbing | ice-hockey | snowboarding |

