.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, watermelon, lemon, lettuce
1. the person eating watermelon is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
3. the person eating lemon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | lemon | lettuce | watermelon | banana |

