1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the firefighter is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the freelancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | doctor | firefighter | fisherman | freelancer |

 